title: Durham's award-winning battery collection returns week of Nov. 2 (Regional Municipality of Durham)
text: ( Source : Regional Municipality of Durham ) Residents received two orange stickers in their 2015 Waste Management Calendars, distributed via Canada Post . Residents should affix the sticker to their own clear, zipper-style plastic bags
